    "created_at": "2015-12-10T05:57:03Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-10T05:57:03Z",
    "body": "> What's wrong with the non-OSX code?\n\nAt least on Window, it doesn't restore the minimized and fullscreen state of windows, and gives focus to wrong windows. (calling `show()` would focus a window)\n\nIf you really want to have fallback code on other platforms, calling `hide()` and `showInactive()` is enough. Users who want other behaviors should write their own code.\n"
  },
