    "created_at": "2015-12-16T04:04:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-16T04:06:40Z",
    "body": "The concept of apps \"Hiding\" on Windows or Linux is pretty weird tbh, I'd also rather this be a no-op on Windows / Linux to encourage app developers not to use it there. \n\nI'd also be :+1: on not providing this as an explicit method at all, just having OS X's windows implicitly handle Cmd-H (perhaps emitting an event that allows an app to cancel it) - this way most devs just get this behavior for free\n"
  },
