    "created_at": "2015-12-16T10:43:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-16T10:43:04Z",
    "body": "> I'd also be :+1: on not providing this as an explicit method at all, just having OS X's windows implicitly handle Cmd-H\n\nThat's how it currently works. I need this method as I want the same behavior of Cmd-H when the window is closed (because I need to keep it in the background).\n\n> perhaps emitting an event that allows an app to cancel it\n\nI guess that could be useful too, but it doesn't solve my problem.\n"
